# ============================================================================
# BATCH PIPELINE SCRIPTS (500-519)
# ============================================================================
#
# These scripts handle batch transcription and orchestration.
#
# Execution order when 515 runs:
#   Phase 1: 512 (scan for missing transcriptions)
#   Phase 2: GPU transcription
#   Phase 3: 520 (diarization on GPU)
#   Phase 4: 518 (postprocess on edge)
#   Phase 5: 524, 525 (enrich - topics & AI)
#   Phase 6: Report
#
# Main entry point: ./scripts/515-run-batch-transcribe.sh
#
# Scripts in this section:
#   512-scan-missing-chunks.sh      - Scan S3 for untranscribed audio
#   515-run-batch-transcribe.sh     - MAIN ORCHESTRATOR
#   518-postprocess-transcripts.sh  - Dedupe, format, update metadata
#
# ============================================================================
